Facebook Page URL, Page Name, Popup width and height, etc. can be adjusted from configuration settings. You can enable/disable Facebook Like Box on Popup. You can also enable/disable Facebook Like Box on left and right sidebar.

Features:-

Easy to install and use
100% Free
